<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Haze Comes"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="霞がついてくる"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Isekaijoucho"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="ヰ世界情緒"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="异世界情绪"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Creation"/><amll:meta key="album" value="創生"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPZ922103287"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="1907752043"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="002QmPEE0lxv6G"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="336304161"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="2IeYMzlpMbZxBjTXvjHHXD"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1688353223"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="3:10.990"><div begin="1.830" end="3:10.990"><p begin="1.830" end="5.260" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1.830" end="2.360">幽</span><span begin="2.360" end="2.810">霊</span><span begin="2.810" end="3.020">屋</span><span begin="3.020" end="3.520">敷</span><span begin="3.520" end="3.740">の</span><span begin="3.740" end="4.180">窓</span><span begin="4.180" end="4.420">か</span><span begin="4.420" end="4.610">ら</span><span begin="4.610" end="4.760">ひ</span><span begin="4.870" end="4.990">と</span><span begin="5.100" end="5.260">つ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">从幽灵宅邸的窗户传来一个</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">從幽靈宅邸的窗戶傳來一個</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">From the window of the haunted mansion one</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">유령 저택 창문에서 하나</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Depuis l&apos;une des fenêtres de la maison hantée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Desde la ventana de la mansión embrujada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Aus dem Fenster der Geistervilla</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">De uma janela da mansão assombrada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Из окна дома с привидениями</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Da una finestra della casa stregata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yuurei yashiki no mado kara hitotsu</span></p><p begin="5.510" end="8.730" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="5.510" end="5.780">知</span><span begin="5.780" end="6.020">ら</span><span begin="6.020" end="6.250">な</span><span begin="6.250" end="6.350">い</span><span begin="6.460" end="6.900">誰</span><span begin="6.900" end="7.150">か</span><span begin="7.150" end="7.350">の</span><span begin="7.350" end="7.840">声</span><span begin="7.840" end="8.010">が</span><span begin="8.010" end="8.280">す</span><span begin="8.280" end="8.730">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">不知是谁的声音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">不知是誰的聲音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Voice of an unknown someone can be heard</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">모르는 누군가의 목소리가 나</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J&apos;entends la voix de quelqu&apos;un que je ne connais pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Se escucha la voz de un desconocido</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ertönt die Stimme von jemand Unbekanntem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ouve-se a voz de alguém desconhecido</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Доносится голос кого-то незнакомого</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Si sente la voce di uno sconosciuto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shiranai dareka no koe ga suru</span></p><p begin="9.140" end="12.530" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="9.140" end="9.170">「</span><span begin="9.170" end="9.880">眼</span><span begin="9.880" end="10.100">を</span><span begin="10.100" end="10.300">向</span><span begin="10.300" end="10.530">け</span><span begin="10.530" end="10.770">た</span><span begin="10.770" end="11.000">ら</span><span begin="11.000" end="11.470">戻</span><span begin="11.470" end="11.680">れ</span><span begin="11.680" end="11.850">は</span><span begin="11.850" end="12.130">し</span><span begin="12.130" end="12.360">な</span><span begin="12.360" end="12.500">い</span><span begin="12.500" end="12.530">」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">「一旦注视便再也无法回头」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">「一旦注視便再也無法回頭」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">&quot;If you turn your eyes you can never return&quot;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">「시선을 주면 돌아올 수 없어」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">« Si tu poses les yeux dessus tu ne pourras plus revenir »</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">«Si lo miras no podrás regresar»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">„Wenn du hinübersiehst gibt es kein Zurück mehr“</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">«Se você olhar não poderá voltar»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">«Если посмотришь туда то уже не вернёшься»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">«Se volgi lo sguardo non potrai più tornare»</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">&quot;Manako o muketara modore wa shinai&quot;</span></p><p begin="12.810" end="15.950" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="12.810" end="12.990">お</span><span begin="12.990" end="13.480">筆</span><span begin="13.480" end="13.680">の</span><span begin="13.680" end="14.100">せん</span><span begin="14.100" end="14.420">せ</span><span begin="14.420" end="14.640">が</span><span begin="14.640" end="14.820">言</span><span begin="14.820" end="15.060">っ</span><span begin="15.060" end="15.310">て</span><span begin="15.310" end="15.440">い</span><span begin="15.550" end="15.950">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">执笔的先生曾这么说过</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">執筆的先生曾這麼說過</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The calligraphy teacher used to say</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">붓글씨 선생님이 말했었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est ce que disait mon maître de calligraphie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Lo decía el maestro del pincel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sagte der Lehrmeister des Pinsels</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O mestre do pincel havia dito</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Так говорил учитель каллиграфии</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Così diceva il maestro di pennello</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ofude no sense ga itte ita</span></p><p begin="16.380" end="19.820" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="16.380" end="16.630">は</span><span begin="16.630" end="16.900">じ</span><span begin="16.900" end="17.140">め</span><span begin="17.140" end="17.380">は</span><span begin="17.380" end="17.610">な</span><span begin="17.610" end="17.800">ん</span><span begin="17.800" end="18.030">だ</span><span begin="18.030" end="18.260">か</span><span begin="18.260" end="18.490">わ</span><span begin="18.490" end="18.730">か</span><span begin="18.730" end="18.970">ら</span><span begin="18.970" end="19.170">な</span><span begin="19.170" end="19.380">か</span><span begin="19.380" end="19.630">っ</span><span begin="19.630" end="19.820">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">一开始完全不明所以</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">一開始完全不明所以</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">At first I did not understand what it was</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">처음엔 뭔지 몰랐어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Au début je ne savais pas ce que c&apos;était</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Al principio no entendía qué era</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Am Anfang wusste ich nicht was es war</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No começo eu não entendia o que era</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Поначалу я не понимала что это</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">All&apos;inizio non capivo cosa fosse</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hajime wa nandaka wakaranakatta</span></p><p begin="20.090" end="23.210" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="20.090" end="20.290">も</span><span begin="20.290" end="20.550">や</span><span begin="20.550" end="20.760">も</span><span begin="20.760" end="20.990">や</span><span begin="20.990" end="21.210">が</span><span begin="21.210" end="21.450">か</span><span begin="21.450" end="21.670">っ</span><span begin="21.670" end="21.910">た</span><span begin="21.910" end="22.140">お</span><span begin="22.140" end="22.580">友</span><span begin="22.580" end="23.210">達</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那位雾蒙蒙的朋友</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那位霧濛濛的朋友</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A hazy clouded friend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">뿌옇게 흐려진 친구</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un ami enveloppé de brume</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un amigo envuelto en niebla</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In Dunst gehüllte Freunde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Um amigo envolto em névoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Окутанный дымкой друг</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Un amico avvolto dalla foschia</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Moyamoya gakatta otomodachi</span></p><p begin="23.670" end="27.070" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="23.670" end="24.180">一</span><span begin="24.180" end="24.410">人</span><span begin="24.410" end="24.650">で</span><span begin="24.650" end="24.860">い</span><span begin="24.860" end="25.100">る</span><span begin="25.100" end="25.330">の</span><span begin="25.330" end="25.510">を</span><span begin="25.510" end="25.950">赦</span><span begin="25.950" end="26.220">し</span><span begin="26.220" end="26.440">て</span><span begin="26.440" end="26.680">く</span><span begin="26.680" end="26.900">れ</span><span begin="26.900" end="27.070">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">宽恕了形单影只的我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">寬恕了形單影隻的我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Allowed me to be all alone</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">혼자 있는 걸 용서해 주었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il m&apos;a pardonné d&apos;être seule</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que me permitió estar sola</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Erlaubten mir allein zu sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que me perdoou por estar sozinha</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Позволил мне оставаться одной</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi ha permesso di stare da sola</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hitori de iru no o yurushite kureta</span></p><p begin="27.290" end="29.760" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="27.290" end="27.800">静</span><span begin="27.800" end="28.050">か</span><span begin="28.050" end="28.260">な</span><span begin="28.260" end="28.680">交</span><span begin="28.680" end="28.940">差</span><span begin="28.940" end="29.760">点</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">寂静的十字路口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">寂靜的十字路口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A quiet intersection</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">조용한 교차로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Au croisement silencieux</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Una intersección tranquila</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eine stille Kreuzung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Um cruzamento silencioso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Тихий перекрёсток</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Un incrocio silenzioso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shizuka na kousaten</span></p><p begin="30.050" end="33.180" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="30.050" end="30.520">青</span><span begin="30.520" end="31.420">空</span><span begin="31.420" end="31.660">は</span><span begin="31.660" end="32.130">深</span><span begin="32.130" end="32.340">い</span><span begin="32.340" end="33.180">青</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">苍穹是深邃的蓝</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">蒼穹是深邃的藍</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The blue sky is a deep blue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">푸른 하늘은 짙은 푸름</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le ciel bleu est d&apos;un bleu profond</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El cielo azul es de un azul profundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der blaue Himmel ist ein tiefes Blau</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O céu azul é de um azul profundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Голубое небо цвета глубокой синевы</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il cielo azzurro è di un blu profondo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aozora wa fukai ao</span></p><p begin="33.470" end="37.280" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="33.470" end="34.170">到</span><span begin="34.170" end="34.620">底</span><span begin="34.620" end="34.850">こ</span><span begin="34.850" end="35.100">こ</span><span begin="35.100" end="35.320">ら</span><span begin="35.320" end="35.540">で</span><span begin="35.540" end="35.820">買</span><span begin="35.820" end="36.000">え</span><span begin="36.000" end="36.200">る</span><span begin="36.200" end="36.660">絵</span><span begin="36.660" end="36.910">の</span><span begin="36.910" end="37.090">具</span><span begin="37.090" end="37.280">じゃ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">仅凭在这一带买到的颜料</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">僅憑在這一帶買到的顏料</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">With the paints you can buy around here anyway</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">도저히 이 근처에서 살 수 있는 물감으론</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Avec les peintures qu&apos;on peut acheter dans le coin de toute façon</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Con las pinturas que puedes comprar por aquí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mit den Farben die man hier so kaufen kann</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Com as tintas que se pode comprar por aqui</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Красками что можно купить в этих краях</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dopotutto con i colori che si comprano da queste parti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Toutei kokora de kaeru enogu ja</span></p><p begin="37.580" end="40.950" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="37.580" end="37.800">描</span><span begin="37.800" end="38.020">き</span><span begin="38.020" end="38.290">き</span><span begin="38.290" end="38.450">る</span><span begin="38.450" end="38.730">っ</span><span begin="38.730" end="38.880">た</span><span begin="38.880" end="39.190">っ</span><span begin="39.190" end="39.530">て</span><span begin="39.640" end="39.860">無</span><span begin="39.860" end="40.300">理</span><span begin="40.300" end="40.520">だ</span><span begin="40.520" end="40.950">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">是绝对无法将其描绘殆尽的哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">是絕對無法將其描繪殆盡的哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It is impossible to paint it perfectly</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">다 그려내기란 무리야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il est impossible de le peindre entièrement</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Es imposible pintarlo por completo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ist es unmöglich es vollständig zu malen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Seria impossível pintar tudo isso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ни за что не удастся это нарисовать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È impossibile dipingerlo per intero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kakikiru ttatte muri da yo</span></p><p begin="41.220" end="44.380" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="41.220" end="41.330">だ</span><span begin="41.440" end="41.690">か</span><span begin="41.690" end="41.810">ら</span><span begin="41.920" end="42.140">み</span><span begin="42.140" end="42.370">ん</span><span begin="42.370" end="42.560">な</span><span begin="42.560" end="43.050">空</span><span begin="43.050" end="43.270">を</span><span begin="43.520" end="43.940">見</span><span begin="43.940" end="44.190">て</span><span begin="44.190" end="44.380">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">所以大家都在仰望天空</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">所以大家都在仰望天空</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That is why everyone looks up at the sky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그래서 다들 하늘을 보고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est pourquoi tout le monde regarde le ciel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Por eso todos miran al cielo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Deshalb schauen alle in den Himmel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Por isso todos estão olhando para o céu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Поэтому все смотрят в небо</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Per questo tutti guardano il cielo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dakara minna sora o miteru</span></p><p begin="44.590" end="48.000" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="44.590" end="45.080">黒</span><span begin="45.080" end="45.270">か</span><span begin="45.270" end="45.990">白</span><span begin="45.990" end="46.430">か</span><span begin="46.430" end="46.690">問</span><span begin="46.690" end="46.910">わ</span><span begin="46.910" end="47.140">れ</span><span begin="47.140" end="47.450">な</span><span begin="47.450" end="47.570">い</span><span begin="47.570" end="47.810">こ</span><span begin="47.810" end="48.000">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">不会被追问是黑还是白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">不會被追問是黑還是白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Not being asked whether it is black or white</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">흑인지 백인지 묻지 않는 것</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le fait qu&apos;on ne demande pas si c&apos;est noir ou blanc</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que no se pregunte si es blanco o negro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nicht gefragt zu werden ob es schwarz oder weiß ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O fato de não ser questionada se é preto ou branco</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">То что никто не спрашивает чёрное это или белое</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il fatto di non dover scegliere tra bianco e nero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kuro ka shiro ka towarenai koto</span></p><p begin="48.220" end="52.090" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="48.220" end="48.500">そ</span><span begin="48.500" end="48.720">れ</span><span begin="48.720" end="48.950">が</span><span begin="48.950" end="49.240">な</span><span begin="49.240" end="49.410">ん</span><span begin="49.410" end="49.620">だ</span><span begin="49.620" end="49.860">か</span><span begin="49.860" end="50.540">心</span><span begin="50.540" end="50.810">地</span><span begin="50.810" end="51.250">良</span><span begin="51.250" end="51.480">か</span><span begin="51.480" end="51.690">っ</span><span begin="51.690" end="52.090">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这点总让人感到无比惬意</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這點總讓人感到無比愜意</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That felt somehow comforting</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그게 왠지 마음이 편했어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;était d&apos;une certaine manière si réconfortant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Eso de alguna manera se sentía reconfortante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das war irgendwie angenehm</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Isso de alguma forma me reconfortava</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">От этого мне было почему-то так уютно</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Era in qualche modo piacevole</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore ga nandaka kokochiyokatta</span></p><p begin="52.310" end="55.910" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="52.310" end="53.040">君</span><span begin="53.040" end="53.230">の</span><span begin="53.240" end="53.740">顔</span><span begin="53.740" end="53.930">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你的容颜也好</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你的容顏也好</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Your face too</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너의 얼굴도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ton visage aussi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tu rostro también</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch dein Gesicht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O seu rosto também</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И твоё лицо</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche il tuo viso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi no kao mo</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="53.230" end="55.910"><span begin="53.230" end="53.690">(る</span><span begin="53.740" end="54.090">る</span><span begin="54.160" end="54.380">る</span><span begin="54.420" end="55.910">る)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">噜噜噜噜</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">嚕嚕嚕嚕</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ru ru ru ru</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">루루루루</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ru ru ru ru</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ru ru ru ru</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lu lu lu lu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ru ru ru ru</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ру-ру-ру-ру</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Lu lu lu lu</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Rurururu</span></span></p><p begin="54.160" end="55.960" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="54.160" end="54.860">君</span><span begin="54.860" end="54.950">の</span><span begin="55.060" end="55.560">声</span><span begin="55.560" end="55.960">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你的声音也罢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你的聲音也罷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Your voice too</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너의 목소리도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ta voix aussi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tu voz también</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch deine Stimme</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A sua voz também</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И твой голос</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche la tua voce</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi no koe mo</span></p><p begin="56.200" end="59.610" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="56.200" end="56.910">霞</span><span begin="56.910" end="57.120">が</span><span begin="57.120" end="57.400">つ</span><span begin="57.400" end="57.580">い</span><span begin="57.580" end="57.830">て</span><span begin="57.830" end="58.060">く</span><span begin="58.060" end="59.610">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">都有霞霭如影随形</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">都有霞靄如影隨形</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The haze follows along</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">안개가 따라와</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La brume nous suit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La bruma nos sigue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der Dunst folgt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A névoa vem nos seguindo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Окутывает туманная дымка</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La foschia li accompagna</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kasumi ga tsuite kuru</span></p><p begin="1:29.080" end="1:32.520" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:29.080" end="1:29.640">行</span><span begin="1:29.640" end="1:30.030">雲</span><span begin="1:30.030" end="1:30.510">淑</span><span begin="1:30.510" end="1:30.770">女</span><span begin="1:30.770" end="1:30.960">の</span><span begin="1:30.960" end="1:31.240">秘</span><span begin="1:31.240" end="1:31.650">密</span><span begin="1:31.650" end="1:31.880">を</span><span begin="1:31.880" end="1:32.320">隠</span><span begin="1:32.320" end="1:32.520">せ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">藏起行云淑女的秘密</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">藏起行雲淑女的秘密</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Hide the secret of the drifting cloud lady</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">떠도는 구름 같은 숙녀의 비밀을 감춰라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Cache les secrets de la dame aux nuages flottants</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Oculta el secreto de la dama de las nubes flotantes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verbirg das Geheimnis der Wolkendame</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esconda o segredo da dama das nuvens flutuantes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Спрячь секрет леди плывущих облаков</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nascondi i segreti della signora delle nuvole fluttuanti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kouun shukujo no himitsu o kakuse</span></p><p begin="1:32.780" end="1:35.940" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:32.780" end="1:33.070">非</span><span begin="1:33.070" end="1:33.300">の</span><span begin="1:33.300" end="1:33.520">あ</span><span begin="1:33.520" end="1:33.740">る</span><span begin="1:33.740" end="1:33.960">と</span><span begin="1:33.960" end="1:34.210">こ</span><span begin="1:34.210" end="1:34.430">ろ</span><span begin="1:34.430" end="1:34.630">に</span><span begin="1:34.630" end="1:35.310">煙</span><span begin="1:35.310" end="1:35.550">あ</span><span begin="1:35.550" end="1:35.940">り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">有过错之地必起烟雾</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">有過錯之地必起煙霧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Where there is a fault there is smoke</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">허물이 있는 곳에 연기가 나지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Là où il y a une faute il y a de la fumée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Donde hay culpa hay humo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wo Schuld ist da ist Rauch</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Onde há falhas há fumaça</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Там где есть вина клубится дым</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dove c&apos;è una colpa c&apos;è fumo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hi no aru tokoro ni kemuri ari</span></p><p begin="1:36.420" end="1:39.830" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:36.420" end="1:36.450">「</span><span begin="1:36.450" end="1:36.680">あ</span><span begin="1:36.680" end="1:36.910">な</span><span begin="1:36.910" end="1:37.130">た</span><span begin="1:37.130" end="1:37.360">に</span><span begin="1:37.360" end="1:37.580">ど</span><span begin="1:37.580" end="1:37.810">こ</span><span begin="1:37.810" end="1:38.040">か</span><span begin="1:38.040" end="1:38.240">で</span><span begin="1:38.240" end="1:38.500">触</span><span begin="1:38.500" end="1:38.710">れ</span><span begin="1:38.710" end="1:38.940">た</span><span begin="1:38.940" end="1:39.180">気</span><span begin="1:39.180" end="1:39.370">が</span><span begin="1:39.370" end="1:39.640">す</span><span begin="1:39.640" end="1:39.800">る</span><span begin="1:39.800" end="1:39.830">」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">「总觉得在哪里触碰过你」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">「總覺得在哪裡觸碰過你」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">&quot;I feel like I have touched you somewhere before&quot;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">「어디선가 당신에게 닿았던 것 같아」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">« J&apos;ai l&apos;impression de t&apos;avoir touché quelque part »</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">«Siento que te he tocado en alguna parte»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">„Ich habe das Gefühl dich irgendwo schon einmal berührt zu haben“</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">«Sinto que já toquei em você em algum lugar»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">«Мне кажется я уже касалась тебя где-то»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">«Ho la sensazione di averti toccato da qualche parte»</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">&quot;Anata ni dokoka de fureta ki ga suru&quot;</span></p><p begin="1:40.070" end="1:42.330" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:40.070" end="1:40.530">輪</span><span begin="1:40.530" end="1:40.760">廻</span><span begin="1:40.760" end="1:41.000">の</span><span begin="1:41.000" end="1:41.220">お</span><span begin="1:41.220" end="1:41.460">ま</span><span begin="1:41.460" end="1:41.670">ま</span><span begin="1:41.670" end="1:41.900">ご</span><span begin="1:41.900" end="1:42.330">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">轮回的过家家游戏</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">輪迴的過家家遊戲</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Playing house of reincarnation</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">윤회의 소꿉놀이</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La dînette de la réincarnation</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un juego de niños sobre la reencarnación</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein kindliches Spiel der Wiedergeburt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Um faz de conta de reencarnação</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Игры в реинкарнацию</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Giocando alla reincarnazione</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Rinne no omamagoto</span></p><p begin="1:42.760" end="1:45.920" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:42.760" end="1:43.060">そ</span><span begin="1:43.060" end="1:43.290">れ</span><span begin="1:43.290" end="1:43.460">も</span><span begin="1:43.460" end="1:43.700">そ</span><span begin="1:43.700" end="1:44.170">う</span><span begin="1:44.170" end="1:44.410">か</span><span begin="1:44.410" end="1:44.650">こ</span><span begin="1:44.650" end="1:44.880">の</span><span begin="1:44.880" end="1:45.300">街</span><span begin="1:45.300" end="1:45.920">じゃ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">说的也是呢 毕竟在这座城市里</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">說的也是呢 畢竟在這座城市裡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I guess that makes sense in this town</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그것도 그런가 이 거리에선</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je suppose que c&apos;est logique dans cette ville</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Supongo que es así en esta ciudad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wohl wahr denn in dieser Stadt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Faz sentido nesta cidade afinal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">А впрочем в этом городе</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E ha senso in questa città</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore mo sou ka kono machi ja</span></p><p begin="1:46.210" end="1:50.000" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:46.210" end="1:46.850">今</span><span begin="1:46.850" end="1:47.320">更</span><span begin="1:47.320" end="1:47.820">人</span><span begin="1:47.820" end="1:48.030">で</span><span begin="1:48.030" end="1:48.270">居</span><span begin="1:48.270" end="1:48.720">よう</span><span begin="1:48.720" end="1:48.920">と</span><span begin="1:48.920" end="1:49.400">す</span><span begin="1:49.400" end="1:49.630">る</span><span begin="1:49.630" end="1:49.870">の</span><span begin="1:49.870" end="1:50.000">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">事到如今还妄想保持人类的模样</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">事到如今還妄想保持人類的模樣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Trying to remain human at this point</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이제 와서 사람으로 남으려 하는 것도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Essayer de rester humaine à ce stade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Intentar seguir siendo humana a estas alturas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jetzt noch ein Mensch sein zu wollen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tentar continuar sendo humano a esta altura</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пытаться оставаться человеком теперь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Cercare di rimanere umani a questo punto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Imasara hito de iyou to suru no mo</span></p><p begin="1:50.300" end="1:53.680" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:50.300" end="1:50.520">馬</span><span begin="1:50.520" end="1:50.790">鹿</span><span begin="1:50.790" end="1:51.000">み</span><span begin="1:51.000" end="1:51.160">た</span><span begin="1:51.160" end="1:51.210">い</span><span begin="1:51.440" end="1:51.600">だ</span><span begin="1:51.600" end="1:51.910">っ</span><span begin="1:51.910" end="1:52.140">て</span><span begin="1:52.140" end="1:52.610">思</span><span begin="1:52.610" end="1:52.830">う</span><span begin="1:52.830" end="1:53.020">ん</span><span begin="1:53.020" end="1:53.250">だ</span><span begin="1:53.250" end="1:53.680">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">想想还真是傻得可怜啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">想想還真是傻得可憐啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Just feels incredibly foolish you know</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">바보 같다고 생각해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je trouve que c&apos;est un peu ridicule</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Creo que parece una estupidez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Kommt mir vor als wäre es idiotisch</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu acho que parece uma idiotice</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Кажется мне такой глупостью</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Penso sia davvero da stupidi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Baka mitai datte omoun da yo</span></p><p begin="1:53.940" end="1:57.130" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:53.940" end="1:54.060">だ</span><span begin="1:54.160" end="1:54.400">か</span><span begin="1:54.400" end="1:54.630">ら</span><span begin="1:54.630" end="1:55.080">僕</span><span begin="1:55.080" end="1:55.280">は</span><span begin="1:55.280" end="1:55.760">君</span><span begin="1:55.760" end="1:55.940">を</span><span begin="1:56.230" end="1:56.660">見</span><span begin="1:56.660" end="1:56.920">て</span><span begin="1:56.920" end="1:57.130">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">所以我注视着你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">所以我注視著你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That is why I am looking at you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그래서 나는 너를 보고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est pourquoi je te regarde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Por eso yo te estoy mirando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Deshalb schaue ich dich an</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Por isso eu estou olhando para você</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Поэтому я смотрю на тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Per questo io ti sto guardando</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dakara boku wa kimi o miteru</span></p><p begin="1:57.330" end="2:00.720" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:57.330" end="1:57.820">黒</span><span begin="1:57.820" end="1:58.040">と</span><span begin="1:58.040" end="1:58.730">黒</span><span begin="1:58.730" end="1:59.180">が</span><span begin="1:59.180" end="1:59.380">混</span><span begin="1:59.380" end="1:59.640">ざ</span><span begin="1:59.640" end="1:59.870">り</span><span begin="1:59.870" end="2:00.190">合</span><span begin="2:00.190" end="2:00.310">う</span><span begin="2:00.310" end="2:00.550">こ</span><span begin="2:00.550" end="2:00.720">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">黑与黑相互交融</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">黑與黑相互交融</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Black and black mixing together</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">흑과 흑이 뒤섞이는 것</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le fait que le noir se mélange au noir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que el negro y el negro se mezclen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass Schwarz und Schwarz sich vermischen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O preto e o preto se misturando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">То что чёрный смешивается с чёрным</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il nero che si mescola col nero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kuro to kuro ga mazariau koto</span></p><p begin="2:00.940" end="2:04.810" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:00.940" end="2:01.240">そ</span><span begin="2:01.240" end="2:01.470">れ</span><span begin="2:01.470" end="2:01.690">は</span><span begin="2:01.690" end="2:02.140">大</span><span begin="2:02.140" end="2:02.590">概</span><span begin="2:02.590" end="2:03.050">意</span><span begin="2:03.050" end="2:03.270">味</span><span begin="2:03.270" end="2:03.510">が</span><span begin="2:03.510" end="2:03.970">な</span><span begin="2:03.970" end="2:04.180">か</span><span begin="2:04.180" end="2:04.420">っ</span><span begin="2:04.420" end="2:04.810">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那大概没有任何意义</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那大概沒有任何意義</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That largely held no meaning</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그건 대개 의미가 없었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ça n&apos;avait généralement aucun sens</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Eso en general no tenía sentido</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das hatte zumeist keine Bedeutung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Isso na maioria das vezes não tinha sentido</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">По большей части не имело смысла</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Fondamentalmente non aveva alcun senso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore wa taigai imi ga nakatta</span></p><p begin="2:05.040" end="2:08.650" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:05.040" end="2:05.200">好</span><span begin="2:05.300" end="2:05.780">き</span><span begin="2:05.780" end="2:05.990">な</span><span begin="2:06.000" end="2:06.210">と</span><span begin="2:06.210" end="2:06.470">こ</span><span begin="2:06.470" end="2:06.660">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">喜欢的地方也好</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">喜歡的地方也好</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The parts I like too</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">좋아하는 점도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les choses que j&apos;aime</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las partes que me gustan también</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch was ich mag</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As partes que eu gosto também</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И то что мне нравится</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche le cose che amo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Suki na toko mo</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="2:05.990" end="2:08.650"><span begin="2:05.990" end="2:06.420">(る</span><span begin="2:06.480" end="2:06.840">る</span><span begin="2:06.890" end="2:07.110">る</span><span begin="2:07.160" end="2:08.650">る)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">噜噜噜噜</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">嚕嚕嚕嚕</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ru ru ru ru</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">루루루루</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ru ru ru ru</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ru ru ru ru</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lu lu lu lu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ru ru ru ru</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ру-ру-ру-ру</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Lu lu lu lu</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Rurururu</span></span></p><p begin="2:06.860" end="2:08.710" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:06.860" end="2:07.150">そ</span><span begin="2:07.150" end="2:07.550">れ</span><span begin="2:07.550" end="2:07.820">以</span><span begin="2:07.820" end="2:08.280">外</span><span begin="2:08.280" end="2:08.710">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">除此以外的也罢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">除此以外的也罷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">And everything else too</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 외의 것도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et tout le reste aussi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y todo lo demás</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und auch alles andere</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E todo o resto também</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И всё остальное</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E tutto il resto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore igai mo</span></p><p begin="2:08.950" end="2:12.300" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:08.950" end="2:09.400">同</span><span begin="2:09.400" end="2:09.640">じ</span><span begin="2:09.640" end="2:09.870">に</span><span begin="2:09.870" end="2:10.090">な</span><span begin="2:10.090" end="2:10.300">っ</span><span begin="2:10.300" end="2:10.540">た</span><span begin="2:10.540" end="2:10.790">か</span><span begin="2:10.790" end="2:12.300">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">都变得毫无二致了啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">都變得毫無二致了啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because they all became the same</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">똑같아졌으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Parce qu&apos;ils sont devenus les mêmes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque se han vuelto lo mismo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weil es das Gleiche geworden ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Porque acabaram se tornando a mesma coisa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ведь всё это стало одинаковым</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perché sono diventati la stessa cosa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Onaji ni natta kara</span></p><p begin="2:33.880" end="2:37.490" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:33.880" end="2:34.400">春</span><span begin="2:34.400" end="2:35.340">風</span><span begin="2:35.340" end="2:35.570">の</span><span begin="2:35.570" end="2:35.780">う</span><span begin="2:35.780" end="2:36.020">ら</span><span begin="2:36.020" end="2:36.240">ら</span><span begin="2:36.240" end="2:36.460">に</span><span begin="2:36.460" end="2:37.110">満</span><span begin="2:37.110" end="2:37.350">ち</span><span begin="2:37.350" end="2:37.490">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">待到春风和煦盈满大地</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">待到春風和煦盈滿大地</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Filled with the gentleness of the spring breeze</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">화창한 봄바람으로 가득 차서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Baignée par la douceur de la brise printanière</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Lleno de la belleza de la brisa primaveral</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Erfüllt von der heiteren Frühlingsbrise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Cheia da beleza da brisa de primavera</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Наполнившись сиянием весеннего ветра</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Riempiendoci del tepore del vento primaverile</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Harukaze no urara ni michite</span></p><p begin="2:37.580" end="2:42.160" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:37.580" end="2:37.830">こ</span><span begin="2:37.830" end="2:38.050">の</span><span begin="2:38.050" end="2:38.710">街</span><span begin="2:38.960" end="2:39.140">の</span><span begin="2:39.140" end="2:39.850">霞</span><span begin="2:39.850" end="2:40.080">が</span><span begin="2:40.080" end="2:40.300">消</span><span begin="2:40.300" end="2:40.540">え</span><span begin="2:40.540" end="2:40.660">て</span><span begin="2:40.660" end="2:40.800">し</span><span begin="2:40.800" end="2:41.220">ま</span><span begin="2:41.220" end="2:41.420">っ</span><span begin="2:41.420" end="2:41.690">た</span><span begin="2:41.690" end="2:42.160">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这座城市的霞霭若消散褪去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這座城市的霞靄若消散褪去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If the haze of this town were to fade away completely</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 거리의 안개가 사라져 버린다면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si la brume de cette ville venait à disparaître</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si la bruma de esta ciudad llegara a desaparecer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn der Dunst dieser Stadt verschwunden ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se a névoa desta cidade acabar desaparecendo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если дымка этого города рассеется</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se la foschia di questa città dovesse scomparire</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono machi no kasumi ga kiete shimattara</span></p><p begin="2:42.590" end="2:45.070" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:42.590" end="2:42.690">ま</span><span begin="2:42.800" end="2:43.410">た</span><span begin="2:43.510" end="2:43.710">逃</span><span begin="2:43.710" end="2:43.850">げ</span><span begin="2:43.950" end="2:44.120">て</span><span begin="2:44.120" end="2:44.400">し</span><span begin="2:44.400" end="2:44.620">ま</span><span begin="2:44.620" end="2:44.840">お</span><span begin="2:44.840" end="2:45.070">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我们就再一次逃离这里吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們就再一次逃離這裡吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Let&apos;s run away again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">다시 도망쳐 버리자</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Enfuyons-nous à nouveau</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Huyamos de nuevo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass uns wieder fortlaufen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vamos fugir de novo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Давай снова сбежим</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Scappiamo via di nuovo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mata nigete shimaou</span></p><p begin="2:45.260" end="2:48.160" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:45.260" end="2:45.550">そ</span><span begin="2:45.550" end="2:45.770">の</span><span begin="2:45.770" end="2:46.200">時</span><span begin="2:46.200" end="2:46.670">選</span><span begin="2:46.670" end="2:46.910">ぶ</span><span begin="2:46.910" end="2:47.110">の</span><span begin="2:47.110" end="2:48.160">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">虽不知到那时</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">雖不知到那時</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">What we will choose at that time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그때 선택하는 건</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce que nous choisirons à ce moment-là</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El color que elijamos en ese momento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Was wir dann wählen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O que vamos escolher nessa hora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Какой цвет мы выберем тогда</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ciò che sceglieremo allora</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono toki erabu no wa</span></p><p begin="2:48.250" end="2:51.630" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:48.250" end="2:48.520">ど</span><span begin="2:48.520" end="2:48.740">ん</span><span begin="2:48.740" end="2:48.920">な</span><span begin="2:48.920" end="2:49.620">色</span><span begin="2:49.620" end="2:50.100">か</span><span begin="2:50.100" end="2:50.300">わ</span><span begin="2:50.300" end="2:50.560">か</span><span begin="2:50.560" end="2:50.780">ら</span><span begin="2:50.780" end="2:51.060">な</span><span begin="2:51.060" end="2:51.210">い</span><span begin="2:51.210" end="2:51.470">け</span><span begin="2:51.470" end="2:51.630">ど</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">会选择怎样的色彩</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">會選擇怎樣的色彩</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I do not know what color it will be but</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어떤 색일지 모르겠지만</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne sais pas de quelle couleur ce sera mais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No sé cuál será pero</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Welche Farbe es sein wird weiß ich nicht aber</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu não sei de que cor será mas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я не знаю но</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non so che colore sarà ma</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Donna iro ka wakaranai kedo</span></p><p begin="2:51.910" end="2:55.220" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:51.910" end="2:52.130">受</span><span begin="2:52.130" end="2:52.370">け</span><span begin="2:52.370" end="2:52.590">入</span><span begin="2:52.590" end="2:53.050">れ</span><span begin="2:53.050" end="2:53.270">て</span><span begin="2:53.270" end="2:53.510">あ</span><span begin="2:53.510" end="2:53.730">げ</span><span begin="2:53.730" end="2:53.970">ら</span><span begin="2:53.970" end="2:54.190">れ</span><span begin="2:54.190" end="2:54.380">る</span><span begin="2:54.380" end="2:54.910">よう</span><span begin="2:54.910" end="2:55.220">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">但为了能将其坦然接纳</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">但為了能將其坦然接納</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">So that we can embrace it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">받아들여 줄 수 있도록</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pour que nous puissions l&apos;accepter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Para que podamos aceptarlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Damit wir sie annehmen können</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Para que possamos aceitá-la</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Чтобы мы смогли принять его</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Affinché io possa accoglierlo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ukeirete agerareru you ni</span></p><p begin="2:55.300" end="2:59.550" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:55.300" end="2:55.680">僕</span><span begin="2:55.780" end="2:55.960">た</span><span begin="2:55.960" end="2:56.210">ち</span><span begin="2:56.210" end="2:56.830">は</span><span begin="2:57.130" end="2:57.610">旅</span><span begin="2:57.610" end="2:57.770">を</span><span begin="2:57.770" end="2:58.050">し</span><span begin="2:58.050" end="2:58.680">て</span><span begin="2:58.680" end="2:58.960">い</span><span begin="2:58.960" end="2:59.550">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我们正踏上旅途</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們正踏上旅途</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">We are on a journey</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리들은 여행을 하고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nous sommes en plein voyage</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nosotras estamos viajando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Befinden wir uns auf einer Reise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Nós estamos viajando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мы продолжаем наше путешествие</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Noi stiamo viaggiando</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokutachi wa tabi o shite iru</span></p><p begin="2:59.840" end="3:03.150" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:59.840" end="3:00.320">顔</span><span begin="3:00.320" end="3:00.540">を</span><span begin="3:00.540" end="3:01.050">隠</span><span begin="3:01.050" end="3:01.260">し</span><span begin="3:01.260" end="3:01.480">た</span><span begin="3:01.480" end="3:01.700">ま</span><span begin="3:01.700" end="3:03.150">ま</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就这样隐藏着面容</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就這樣隱藏著面容</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Keeping our faces hidden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">얼굴을 숨긴 채로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tout en gardant nos visages cachés</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Con los rostros ocultos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Gesichter weiterhin verborgen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mantendo os nossos rostos escondidos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Не открывая своих лиц</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tenendo il viso nascosto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kao o kakushita mama</span></p><p begin="3:07.110" end="3:10.990" itunes:key="L39" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:07.110" end="3:07.810">霞</span><span begin="3:07.810" end="3:08.020">が</span><span begin="3:08.020" end="3:08.290">つ</span><span begin="3:08.290" end="3:08.520">い</span><span begin="3:08.520" end="3:08.700">て</span><span begin="3:08.700" end="3:08.960">く</span><span begin="3:08.960" end="3:10.990">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">霞霭如影随形</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">霞靄如影隨形</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The haze follows along</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">안개가 따라와</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La brume nous suit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La bruma nos sigue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der Dunst folgt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A névoa vem nos seguindo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И за нами следует туманная дымка</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La foschia ci accompagna</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kasumi ga tsuite kuru</span></p></div></body></tt>